// VSCode REST Client file (install "REST Client" extension).
@base = http://localhost:3000

### Criar leilão
POST {{base}}/leiloes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "titulo": "Leilão Teste",
  "status": "aberto",
  "precoInicial": 100,
  "precoAtual": 100,
  "valor_incremento": 5,
  "terminaEm": "2030-12-31T23:59:59.000Z",
  "vendedorId": 1
}

### Listar
GET {{base}}/leiloes?titulo=Teste&status=aberto&page=1&limit=10

### Dar lance (troque :id)
POST {{base}}/leiloes/:id/lances
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_usuario": 2,
  "valor": 120
}

### Encerrar
PATCH {{base}}/leiloes/:id/encerrar

### Meus leilões ativos
GET {{base}}/leiloes/me/ativos?usuarioId=1

### Vencidos por mim
GET {{base}}/leiloes/me/vencidos?usuarioId=2
